WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:02.333
Village Chief, don't kick us out

2
00:00:02.333 --> 00:00:03.666
If we get kicked out

3
00:00:03.666 --> 00:00:05.366
How can a family live?

4
00:00:05.966 --> 00:00:06.733
Xiao Zhou

5
00:00:06.733 --> 00:00:09.133
Don't let the village chief kick us out of the village

6
00:00:09.133 --> 00:00:10.200
Really kicked out

7
00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:11.933
We can only beg for food

8
00:00:11.933 --> 00:00:13.766
You just bullied 3 children

9
00:00:13.766 --> 00:00:16.466
When they scold them for being lonely and widowed, when they have a mother and no mother

10
00:00:16.466 --> 00:00:19.100
Didn't you think how much damage it would do to them?

11
00:00:19.100 --> 00:00:21.466
This Deng happened to be wrong.

12
00:00:21.466 --> 00:00:23.066
I shouldn't have hit you

13
00:00:23.066 --> 00:00:25.866
I shouldn't have called you sons.

14
00:00:25.866 --> 00:00:28.166
No, I learned that from my grandmother

15
00:00:28.166 --> 00:00:30.500
Damn child, what nonsense are you talking about?

16
00:00:30.566 --> 00:00:32.333
When did I scold them?

17
00:00:32.333 --> 00:00:33.966
With you, there is me

18
00:00:33.966 --> 00:00:34.966
Don't beg for food

19
00:00:34.966 --> 00:00:36.833
I don't want to go hungry either.

20
00:00:38.366 --> 00:00:40.700
Mom is terribly hungry

21
00:00:43.066 --> 00:00:44.400
This is the last time.

22
00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:46.700
Next time I won't intrude

23
00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:50.666
Xiao Zhou, please get busy with your home affairs first.

24
00:00:50.666 --> 00:00:52.666
We'll see you another day.

25
00:00:52.666 --> 00:00:54.700
You work first, I'll go first

26
00:01:07.500 --> 00:01:08.666
It's all my fault

27
00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:11.766
I neglected you on weekdays

28
00:01:12.333 --> 00:01:13.200
Mr. Zhu

29
00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:15.300
Didn't you just mention the motorcycle today?

30
00:01:15.300 --> 00:01:17.466
Take Xiaodong Xiaohan for a ride

31
00:01:17.466 --> 00:01:19.166
Dad, okay?

32
00:01:19.300 --> 00:01:20.966
You can go.

33
00:02:08.766 --> 00:02:09.566
Ah!

34
00:02:10.100 --> 00:02:11.766
Yeah, Ji, what are you doing?

